  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Father-- father going out early in the morning, walking for miles to a potato field and standing in the sun, digging and-- and sowing and then-- and digging up the potatoes because if he wouldn't bring in the potatoes in time, wintertime [INAUDIBLE] with nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody-- nobody did them any wrong, but nobody did any good, either.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were on their own.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were send off, go for you life, do what you can.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had to make the best.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they managed to somehow scrape money together and buy a cow, and had milk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And milk was not only a commodity to eat, it was a commodity of exchange.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For the milk they could get potatoes from somebody else, or they could get something, or they could get a shirt, or could get something like that, and so on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I've congratulated them on the addition to the family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a major addition to the family, a cow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] say that we will be running a cow and to be [INAUDIBLE] such a precious thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My mother had to go to collect firewood in the wood and bring on -- on her back, carry a bundle of firewood as you see peasant women in Vietnam [INAUDIBLE], and so on.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Those were the images.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And four-- four young children to be educated there in such circumstances.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were starving at times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were starving at times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Apart from the uncertainties of the regime, apart from you never knew what happens there next in terms of-- of-- of the communist order.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were-- they were because anybody who worked for the government was always at the-- at the-- at the peril because nothing in the government offices was 100%.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
